Expected benefit payments are estimated using the same assumptions used in determining our benefit obligation at December 31, 2020.
Because benefit payments will depend on future employment and compensation levels; average years employed; average life spans; and
payment elections, among other factors, changes in any of these assumptions could significantly affect these expected amounts. The
following table provides expected benefit payments under our pension and postretirement plans:
