The sales of receivables did not have a material impact on our consolidated statements of income or to “Total Assets” reported on our
consolidated balance sheets. We reflect cash receipts on sold receivables as cash flows from operations in our consolidated statements of
cash flows. Cash receipts on the deferred purchase price are classified as cash flows from investing activities.
